Dialogue: 0,0:10:14.06,0:10:16.75,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,解除护盾 放他们进战场
Dialogue: 0,0:10:17.22,0:10:19.08,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,要联手作战吗
Dialogue: 0,0:10:22.16,0:10:24.87,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,一号机负责上空 二号机支援火枪型
Dialogue: 0,0:10:25.25,0:10:27.37,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我去帮那个挥剑的
Dialogue: 0,0:10:27.78,0:10:28.65,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,明白
Dialogue: 0,0:10:29.15,0:10:30.59,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,终于能参战了
Dialogue: 0,0:10:36.94,0:10:37.89,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好快
Dialogue: 0,0:10:50.96,0:10:53.72,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那个速度竟能击中 好身手
Dialogue: 0,0:11:10.36,0:11:12.23,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哟 打扰了
Dialogue: 0,0:11:12.71,0:11:14.40,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这些家伙来干嘛啊
Dialogue: 0,0:11:19.10,0:11:21.08,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什么 是来帮忙的吗
Dialogue: 0,0:12:14.75,0:12:17.42,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,用头部攻击的吗 那机体
Dialogue: 0,0:12:20.62,0:12:21.54,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,阿晖
Dialogue: 0,0:12:38.59,0:12:41.77,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,还是不能和你们相互理解啊
Dialogue: 0,0:12:47.13,0:12:49.05,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,确认敌人消灭
Dialogue: 0,0:12:51.38,0:12:53.93,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,所罗门有应答 这是什么
Comment: 0,0:00:00.00,0:00:00.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,//----------------------------TEXTB----------------------------
Dialogue: 0,0:13:00.79,0:13:03.28,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,喂 阵内
Dialogue: 0,0:13:03.57,0:13:04.99,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这里这里
Dialogue: 0,0:13:05.22,0:13:08.70,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,大叔 这就过去…
Dialogue: 0,0:13:11.16,0:13:12.07,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎么了？
Dialogue: 0,0:13:19.82,0:13:22.10,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是Festum…？
Dialogue: 0,0:13:22.45,0:13:25.14,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎么…会那么巨大
Dialogue: 0,0:13:29.53,0:13:31.12,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,追来了吗
Dialogue: 0,0:13:40.59,0:13:43.46,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,所罗门沉默 消失了
Dialogue: 0,0:13:44.28,0:13:47.29,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,看来我们让相当重要的存在上了岛啊
Dialogue: 0,0:13:48.47,0:13:49.90,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,解除战场
Dialogue: 0,0:13:50.63,0:13:52.35,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,迎接来访者吧
Dialogue: 0,0:13:57.09,0:13:58.85,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在干什么 返航吧
Dialogue: 0,0:13:59.73,0:14:02.58,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可是 我可不信任那些家伙
Dialogue: 0,0:14:02.79,0:14:03.86,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,别忘了
Dialogue: 0,0:14:04.14,0:14:06.93,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,驾驶Fafner越久越容易受同化现象侵袭
Dialogue: 0,0:14:07.41,0:14:08.84,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,回来接受检查吧
Dialogue: 0,0:14:08.96,0:14:09.96,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是
Dialogue: 0,0:14:10.80,0:14:12.70,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,十二号机 返航
Dialogue: 0,0:14:13.31,0:14:15.22,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,来 没事吧 阿晖
Dialogue: 0,0:14:15.32,0:14:16.90,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,谢谢 帮大忙了
Dialogue: 0,0:14:19.21,0:14:21.11,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,回来了就开反省会
Dialogue: 0,0:14:21.31,0:14:22.63,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,此前要先进行检查
Dialogue: 0,0:14:29.19,0:14:31.71,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真难受啊 只能看着
Dialogue: 0,0:14:33.22,0:14:34.24,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,…嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:14:41.94,0:14:45.06,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,终于到了 D岛
Dialogue: 0,0:14:45.42,0:14:48.06,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这里的星核 是空气啊
Dialogue: 0,0:14:51.91,0:14:54.38,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,它接受我们了
Dialogue: 0,0:14:57.69,0:14:58.80,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,空气…
Dialogue: 0,0:14:59.14,0:15:01.17,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,最新锐机都报废了
Dialogue: 0,0:15:01.29,0:15:03.74,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,还活着就该谢天谢地啦
Dialogue: 0,0:15:04.11,0:15:04.81,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,队长
Dialogue: 0,0:15:04.99,0:15:07.65,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哦 将陵 辛苦你看家了
Dialogue: 0,0:15:10.17,0:15:12.25,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,您当部队是什么啊
Dialogue: 0,0:15:13.00,0:15:15.20,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,还把真矢也卷进去
Dialogue: 0,0:15:15.41,0:15:18.74,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不要把指挥都丢给阵内前辈 您也靠点谱吧
Dialogue: 0,0:15:20.07,0:15:24.07,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是…非常抱歉 将陵参谋长
Dialogue: 0,0:15:28.92,0:15:31.03,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我是人类军统括总部所属
Dialogue: 0,0:15:31.12,0:15:33.26,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,纳雷因·怀斯曼·博斯上将
Dialogue: 0,0:15:33.60,0:15:35.15,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,感谢贵官的接纳
Dialogue: 0,0:15:35.61,0:15:38.71,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我是龙宫岛ALVIS司令官 真壁史彦
Dialogue: 0,0:15:39.17,0:15:42.34,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,现在人类军直接由将校统率部队了吗
Dialogue: 0,0:15:42.85,0:15:45.29,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,如今光上将就有上百人
Dialogue: 0,0:15:45.57,0:15:47.53,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,军阶已经毫无意义了
Dialogue: 0,0:15:47.96,0:15:51.70,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,尚未失去希望的生者就要背负责任
Dialogue: 0,0:15:51.92,0:15:52.96,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,同感 
Dialogue: 0,0:15:53.39,0:15:57.61,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,为了解除武装 我们需要监视Fafner驾驶员
Dialogue: 0,0:15:58.00,0:16:01.93,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,理所应当 就是他们三人和我
Dialogue: 0,0:16:02.23,0:16:03.73,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,您也能驾驶Fafner吗
Dialogue: 0,0:16:04.27,0:16:08.75,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,身为史上最高龄驾驶员 是我小小的骄傲
Dialogue: 0,0:16:09.51,0:16:13.54,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,请求您批准驾驶员之间的交流
Dialogue: 0,0:16:13.83,0:16:15.56,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,您就是真壁吗
Dialogue: 0,0:16:15.82,0:16:16.49,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什么？
Dialogue: 0,0:16:16.64,0:16:19.14,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不是 他不是一骑·真壁啦
Dialogue: 0,0:16:19.36,0:16:20.10,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,一骑？
Dialogue: 0,0:16:20.33,0:16:23.19,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,对 就是那个超级王牌驾驶员
Dialogue: 0,0:16:23.41,0:16:26.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,将真壁因子传给我们的人
Dialogue: 0,0:16:26.47,0:16:29.11,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,他是破坏了北极星核的驾驶员吧
Dialogue: 0,0:16:29.39,0:16:31.43,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,他是我们的英雄
Dialogue: 0,0:16:32.32,0:16:35.11,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,D岛的一骑·真壁
Dialogue: 0,0:16:39.64,0:16:40.45,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,一骑？
Dialogue: 0,0:16:41.08,0:16:43.05,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,卡诺恩 辛苦了
Dialogue: 0,0:16:43.30,0:16:44.94,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你怎么来这里了
Dialogue: 0,0:16:45.60,0:16:48.54,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就是想看看它
Dialogue: 0,0:16:49.00,0:16:50.27,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,想驾驶吗
Dialogue: 0,0:16:50.77,0:16:52.03,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不是啦
Dialogue: 0,0:16:52.63,0:16:56.14,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你已经战斗得够多了 已经太多了
Dialogue: 0,0:16:56.59,0:16:59.67,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,没人来驾驶Mk.Sein呢
Dialogue: 0,0:17:00.45,0:17:02.38,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,它太特殊了 没人能乘
Dialogue: 0,0:17:02.79,0:17:06.87,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,等成功取出结晶核 就准备沉到海底去
Dialogue: 0,0:17:07.40,0:17:08.47,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是吗
Dialogue: 0,0:17:11.51,0:17:15.25,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不行 这家伙会吸取驾驶者的生命
Dialogue: 0,0:17:16.97,0:17:18.32,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,别再接近它了
Dialogue: 0,0:17:18.94,0:17:19.87,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,拜托了
Dialogue: 0,0:17:20.37,0:17:21.27,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,卡诺恩
Dialogue: 0,0:17:21.33,0:17:24.12,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,拜托也不行的话 我就用武力阻止你
Dialogue: 0,0:17:31.44,0:17:33.87,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你的手可真暖
Dialogue: 0,0:17:36.62,0:17:38.51,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,抱歉打扰了 卡诺恩
Dialogue: 0,0:17:59.30,0:18:01.59,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,战斗之后来瓶这个真是太爽了
Dialogue: 0,0:18:01.82,0:18:05.70,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,唉 真是不想当驾驶员了
Dialogue: 0,0:18:05.99,0:18:08.34,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可是一想到接下来就轮到后辈
Dialogue: 0,0:18:08.49,0:18:10.63,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就觉得不得不继续
Dialogue: 0,0:18:11.05,0:18:12.27,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是啊
Dialogue: 0,0:18:12.49,0:18:18.17,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,剑司学长也一直为了我们而驾驶Fafner
Dialogue: 0,0:18:21.43,0:18:23.05,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,镇痛剂会上瘾的
Dialogue: 0,0:18:23.36,0:18:24.62,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,远见老师说你要是还会痛
Dialogue: 0,0:18:24.77,0:18:28.02,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就跟阿晖一起接受脉冲治疗吧
Dialogue: 0,0:18:28.17,0:18:29.12,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,知道了
Dialogue: 0,0:18:30.39,0:18:32.52,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,呐 美羽在ALVIS里？
Dialogue: 0,0:18:32.57,0:18:33.98,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯…呜哇
Dialogue: 0,0:18:34.24,0:18:36.44,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,还是要让她跟人类军见面吗
Dialogue: 0,0:18:36.57,0:18:37.90,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,听 听说是这样
Dialogue: 0,0:18:38.06,0:18:39.81,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,远见 你先穿好衣服啊
Dialogue: 0,0:18:43.08,0:18:46.14,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎么了 你们俩不都是医生吗
Dialogue: 0,0:18:46.27,0:18:47.39,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真是太嫩了
Dialogue: 0,0:18:47.55,0:18:48.91,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你这人啊
Dialogue: 0,0:18:49.15,0:18:50.64,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,问题不在这里
Dialogue: 0,0:18:51.61,0:18:53.01,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,呐 还没来吗
Dialogue: 0,0:18:53.28,0:18:55.70,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,呐妈妈 妈妈
Dialogue: 0,0:18:55.84,0:18:58.48,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,马上就来 乖乖等着哦
Dialogue: 0,0:18:58.65,0:19:01.79,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,美羽等了好久好久哦
Dialogue: 0,0:19:17.95,0:19:19.04,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,艾米莉
Dialogue: 0,0:19:19.50,0:19:20.70,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,终于见面了呢
Dialogue: 0,0:19:24.08,0:19:25.60,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我相信你一定存在的
Dialogue: 0,0:19:25.75,0:19:29.15,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,绝对绝对不是我的空想
Dialogue: 0,0:19:29.42,0:19:32.47,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯 美羽就在这里哦
Dialogue: 0,0:19:36.38,0:19:39.72,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,相隔天涯的两人却能意识沟通吗
Dialogue: 0,0:19:40.06,0:19:42.47,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这是经由星核中介产生的奇迹
Dialogue: 0,0:19:42.65,0:19:44.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你说星核？
Dialogue: 0,0:19:44.23,0:19:46.25,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就是Festum的思考中枢
Dialogue: 0,0:19:46.43,0:19:49.89,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可变化成万物的超万能构造体
Dialogue: 0,0:19:50.10,0:19:52.65,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我还以为您更了解呢
Dialogue: 0,0:19:53.15,0:19:55.69,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那位少女也能与星核通信吗
Dialogue: 0,0:19:56.08,0:19:59.34,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,似乎是她的弟弟偶然获得了碎片
Dialogue: 0,0:19:59.98,0:20:02.58,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是北极星核的部分幸存体吧
Dialogue: 0,0:20:03.02,0:20:07.30,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,听说艾米莉的弟弟教会了她与那碎片对话的方法
Dialogue: 0,0:20:07.82,0:20:09.51,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,她弟弟现在何处
Dialogue: 0,0:20:10.59,0:20:13.99,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,此前 她所在的城市化为战场
Dialogue: 0,0:20:14.68,0:20:17.89,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,她的弟弟似乎通过星核的碎片
Dialogue: 0,0:20:18.01,0:20:20.33,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,呼吁对方停止杀戮
Dialogue: 0,0:20:20.80,0:20:22.53,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,还与Festum对话了吗
Dialogue: 0,0:20:22.84,0:20:25.39,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是的 敌人退却了
Dialogue: 0,0:20:26.37,0:20:30.03,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,然而作为代价 她的弟弟和家人却被星核同化了
Dialogue: 0,0:20:31.47,0:20:35.04,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,为何只有她幸存这点还是谜
Dialogue: 0,0:20:36.32,0:20:39.87,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,只是 像她一样能与星核通信的人
Dialogue: 0,0:20:40.25,0:20:42.80,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我们称之为「Esperanto」
Dialogue: 0,0:20:43.36,0:20:44.25,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,「希望」…
Dialogue: 0,0:20:44.76,0:20:48.31,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,对 是人类发明的人工语言之名
Dialogue: 0,0:20:48.63,0:20:52.51,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,为了彼此理解 消除纷争而创造的语言
Dialogue: 0,0:20:52.95,0:20:54.46,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是真正的希望
Dialogue: 0,0:21:05.63,0:21:07.33,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,果然已经开门了
Dialogue: 0,0:21:07.69,0:21:08.69,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,远见
Dialogue: 0,0:21:09.37,0:21:11.83,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,商店街都还没开门呢
Dialogue: 0,0:21:12.11,0:21:13.71,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,远见你就歇着吧
Dialogue: 0,0:21:14.00,0:21:14.90,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,没事
Dialogue: 0,0:21:15.12,0:21:16.84,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,大家检查完了都会来的
Dialogue: 0,0:21:18.76,0:21:21.41,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,沟口叔呢 有外卖
Dialogue: 0,0:21:21.67,0:21:24.18,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,说要开会 我去吧
Dialogue: 0,0:21:24.46,0:21:26.07,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不用 我去就好…
Dialogue: 0,0:21:26.49,0:21:27.30,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,打扰了
Dialogue: 0,0:21:27.60,0:21:29.83,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,一骑…在吧
Dialogue: 0,0:21:30.35,0:21:32.18,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,阵内叔 怎么了
Dialogue: 0,0:21:32.55,0:21:35.79,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是真壁司令的指示 我带客人来了
Dialogue: 0,0:21:35.97,0:21:37.03,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,爸爸的？
Dialogue: 0,0:21:39.88,0:21:43.78,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,艾西瓦娅·菲因 珀耳修斯中队Fafner驾驶员
Dialogue: 0,0:21:44.12,0:21:46.72,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,请叫我艾 一骑·真壁
Dialogue: 0,0:21:46.98,0:21:48.55,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎么知道我的名字…
Dialogue: 0,0:21:51.00,0:21:53.34,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,比利·摩根 也是驾驶员
Dialogue: 0,0:21:55.34,0:21:58.08,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,珀耳修斯中队Fafner队队长
Dialogue: 0,0:21:58.39,0:22:00.10,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,乔纳森·光弘·巴特蓝
Dialogue: 0,0:22:01.08,0:22:02.07,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,光弘…
Dialogue: 0,0:22:05.89,0:22:08.42,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,能见到传说中的英雄 我十分感动
Dialogue: 0,0:22:08.84,0:22:12.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,多亏了您 我才能战斗
Dialogue: 0,0:22:12.11,0:22:13.39,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哎 我…？
Dialogue: 0,0:22:13.47,0:22:14.46,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,太棒了
Dialogue: 0,0:22:14.79,0:22:17.94,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,没想到真能见到真壁因子的提供者
Dialogue: 0,0:22:18.10,0:22:19.10,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,因子？
Dialogue: 0,0:22:20.34,0:22:21.78,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你将会知晓
Dialogue: 0,0:22:22.42,0:22:24.52,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不同希望的相遇 
Dialogue: 0,0:22:24.85,0:22:27.15,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,并非必将通往和平
